    dc:creator "Tshernyshev, Sergei E." ;
    dc:date "2012" ;
    dc:title "Two new species of soft-winged flower beetles of the genus Kuatunia Evers, 1945 48 (Coleoptera, Malachiidae) from China and northeastern Russia" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.214749>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.214746>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.214747> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.214749>
    dc:description "FIGURES 15 – 24. Apices of male elytra of Kuatunia species, 15 K. australis Wittmer, 1991, 16 K. bullosa Wittmer 1995, 17 K. emeiensis Wittmer, 1995, 18 K. guilinensis Wittmer, 1995, 19 K. klapperichi Evers, 1945 – 48, 20 K. nigroopaca Wittmer, 1995, 21 K. oblongula (Kiesenwetter, 1874), 22 K. oloyensis Wittmer, 1999, 23 K. sichuana Wittmer, 1995, 24 K. soppongensis Wittmer, 1995. Scale bar 0.5 mm. 15 from Wittmer, 1991; 16 – 20, 23, 24 from Wittmer, 1995; 21 from Wittmer, 1954; 22 from Wittmer, 1999." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/214749/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.214746>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1 – 7. Kuatunia nordica Tshernyshev, 2012 sp. n., 1 male, habitus, 2 apex of right elytra, 3 appendage in elytral apex, 4 apical tergite, 5 apical sternite, 6 tegmen, 7 aedeagus, lateral. Scale bar 1.0 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/214746/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.214747>
    dc:description "FIGURES 8 – 13. Kuatunia wolongensis Tshernyshev, 2012 sp. n., 8 male, habitus, 9 apex of right elytra, 10 apical tergite, 11 apical sternite, 12 tegmen, 13 aedeagus, lateral. Scale bar 1.0 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/214747/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

